02:03:39,800 --> 02:03:41,700
- C'est sûr.
- Ouverture A1.

1464
02:03:52,000 --> 02:03:53,100
Tu la tiens ?

1465
02:03:59,100 --> 02:04:01,700
Barre-toi avant que ça explose.

1466
02:04:05,100 --> 02:04:06,900
Attention, dehors,

1467
02:04:06,900 --> 02:04:08,000
dans l'espace.

1468
02:04:12,300 --> 02:04:14,300
